 Everything by me (doors, docs, etc) are copyrighted (c) GREMLiNS MAXsWARE
 Use this door at your own risk, it's provided as is... So don't blame me!

 Fluffy Net via the  BBS community is slowly dying  and I'd name a few who
 have caused this to happen,  but I s'pose who cares.. except a few of us!
 It's sad to see a great world network like Fluffy Net lose it's users and
 all that, but all things must and will come to an end.. not fuck'n yet!

 I wish everybody around the world all the best for 1999, have fun!  Zeffy
 and I have planned to travel to UK, Europe and USA in March 2000 and hope
 to travel, work and holiday over there for 6 to 12 months.  So now all we
 need to do is save, save and save... and organise everything! Oh goody.

 Happy New Year...

@endnode
